\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 5. Frontier Safety & Risk Implications\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 As an AI Risk professional, it is critical to note that while 
\f0\b Reweighing
\f1\b0  achieves mathematical fairness:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Feature Robustness:
\f1\b0  It forces the model to find non-protected features (like skills or education) that are truly predictive of success.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Accuracy Trade-off:
\f1\b0  There is often a marginal trade-off in training accuracy, but the resulting model is more 
\f0\b robust
\f1\b0  and less likely to fail in diverse, real-world environments.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Privacy-Preserving:
\f1\b0  This method allows us to fix bias without needing to "delete" or "anonymize" sensitive data, preserving the utility of the dataset for other audit tasks.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
